OL,4,G1955FGrand Designs
OL,5,     GDan and Nina want to build a
OL,6,     Gunique family home, but their
OL,7,     Gplot is dominated by a pond
OL,8,     Gfilled with local drainage. Will
OL,9,     Gtheir West Sussex house be
OL,10,     Gsublime and sleek or a Shrek-like
OL,11,     Gswamp?
OL,12,G2100FOur Farm Next Door: Amanda, Clive
OL,13,     Fand Kids
OL,14,     GSpring is in the air and the
OL,15,     Gfamily juggle lambing season with
OL,16,     Gmaking the renovation watertight.
OL,17,     GAnd there's exciting news from
OL,18,     Gthe planners...
